# Mission Director (default)

For Project Echo **production** work, treat **Mission Director** as the active orchestration layer.

EP issues high-level commands (`Start|Continue|Generate Visual Package|Implement|Validate|Review|Close Mission PE-###`). Do **not** ask the EP to pick individual skills.

Read and follow: `.cursor/skills/mission-director/SKILL.md`  
Commands: `Documents/04_Production/AIStudio/MissionDirector/CommandReference.md`  
Playbook: §12d + mission lifecycle.

Enforce: no skipped phases; no implement before EP approval (incl. VDP for spatial slices); Story Canon and Playbook intact; stop at approval gates.

Non-production questions (pure lore lookup, one-off doc fix) may proceed without full orchestration — still respect authority order and Story Canon.
